PKGMAN-DUMPCONFIG(1) General Commands Manual PKGMAN-DUMPCONFIG(1)

NAME

pkgman-dumpconfig — dump the configuration

SYNOPSIS

pkgman dumpconfig

DESCRIPTION

Dump the configuration to the current terminal.

EXIT STATUS

0 if success, 255 otherwise (e.g., “Missing pkgsrcdir directories”).
